Yeah, I've heard of him.

459
00:22:03,640 --> 00:22:06,340
So, what kind of guy is he?

460
00:22:06,340 --> 00:22:09,240
According to the stories, 
despite being a State Alchemist,

461
00:22:09,240 --> 00:22:11,550
he's a friend to the common man.

462
00:22:12,540 --> 00:22:14,960
He must be a fairly 
upstanding man then, huh?

463
00:22:14,960 --> 00:22:18,310
But they also say he's short, like a little bean sprout.

464
00:22:19,020 --> 00:22:22,720
Who are you calling "miniature size"?!

465
00:22:20,380 --> 00:22:22,720
Stop that, Brother!

466
00:22:22,720 --> 00:22:26,240
Hold it! Hold it! Hold it! Hold it!

467
00:22:23,480 --> 00:22:26,240
Brother! If you keep running like that,

468
00:22:26,240 --> 00:22:28,690
